<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }
        .header {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo-text {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #025864;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .tagline {
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 30px 40px 30px;
        }
        .reset-title {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #fff7ed;
            border-left: 4px solid #f97316;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .security-notice p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #9a3412;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #025864;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #013a42;
        }
        .otp-box {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            color: #0f172a;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                <tr>
                    <td align="center" valign="middle">
                        <svg width="24" height="32" viewBox="0 0 36 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="display: block;">
                            <path d="M0 7.5H28.8C31.3202 7.5 32.5804 7.5 33.543 7.99047C34.3897 8.4219 35.0781 9.11031 35.5095 9.95704C36 10.9196 36 12.1798 36 14.7V16.5H7.2C4.67976 16.5 3.41965 16.5 2.45704 16.0095C1.61031 15.5781 0.921901 14.8897 0.490471 14.043C0 13.0804 0 11.8202 0 9.3V7.5Z" fill="#025864"/>
                            <path d="M0 28.5H28.8C31.3202 28.5 32.5804 28.5 33.543 28.0095C34.3897 27.5781 35.0781 26.8897 35.5095 26.043C36 25.0804 36 23.8202 36 21.3V19.5H7.2C4.67976 19.5 3.41965 19.5 2.45704 19.9905C1.61031 20.4219 0.921901 21.1103 0.490471 21.957C0 22.9196 0 24.1798 0 26.7V28.5Z" fill="#025864"/>
                            <path d="M14 31.5H28.8C31.3202 31.5 32.5804 31.5 33.543 31.9905C34.3897 32.4219 35.0781 33.1103 35.5095 33.957C36 34.9196 36 36.1798 36 38.7V40.5H21.2C18.6798 40.5 17.4196 40.5 16.457 40.0095C15.6103 39.5781 14.9219 38.8897 14.4905 38.043C14 37.0804 14 35.8202 14 33.3V31.5Z" fill="#025864"/>
                        </svg>
                    </td>
                    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="padding-left: 12px;">
                        <span class="logo-text">RippliFy</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <div class="tagline">Secure Payment Links for Modern Businesses</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="reset-title">Password Reset Request</h2>
            
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your RippliFy account associated with <strong>{{email}}</strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <p><strong>Security Note:</strong> If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team if you have concerns about your account security.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>To reset your password, please use the following verification code. This code will expire in {{expiresIn}} for security reasons.</p>
            
            <div class="otp-box">{{resetToken}}</div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <h3 style="color: #025864; font-size: 18px;">Password Security Tips:</h3>
            
            <ul style="color: #475569; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li><strong>Use a strong password</strong> - At least 12 characters with mix of letters, numbers, and symbols</li>
                <li><strong>Avoid common passwords</strong> - Don't use easily guessable information</li>
                <li><strong>Use a password manager</strong> - Consider using a secure password manager</li>
                <li><strong>Enable two-factor authentication</strong> - Add an extra layer of security</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you continue to have problems, please contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>The RippliFy Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{currentYear}} RippliFy. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>RippliFy Inc. | Nairobi, Kenya</p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11px;">
                <p>You received this email because a password reset was requested for your RippliFy account.</p>
                <p><a href="#" style="color: #64748b;">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="#" style="color: #64748b;">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#" style="color: #64748b;">Terms of Service</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>